    public class CameraSystemImpl
extends ImageSensorSystemImpl
implements CameraSystem
    An implementation of the model object 'Camera System'.

    The following features are implemented:

    • Width
    • Height
    • Alpha u
    • Alpha v
    • U0
    • V0
    • Color format
    • Translate
    • Rotate
